Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: US v UK elections
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bxnw
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 6 May 1979
UK elections become 'Americanised' as the public relations men move in. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.